Homepage: file:///usr/share/joker-theme/README.md
Description: Joker desktop theme for GNOME (Debian)
 Dark Joker-inspired theme pack: void black, royal purple, and toxic green.
 .
 Includes wallpapers, GTK3/GTK4 CSS overrides, GNOME settings helpers,
 Plymouth boot splash, GDM login screen styling, and a Brave browser theme.
 .
 After install, run: joker-theme
 For Brave: joker-brave-theme --force-quit
